				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Few things...
<br />

<br />
The question asked has no bearin on new or old sorcerors, it was merely which line needed more meat added to it.
<br />

<br />
It was NOT which ones needed fixed.
<br />

<br />
It was NOT what would sorcerors like to see added to the class.
<br />

<br />
A disguise type spell will likely never happen. I woudln't mind seeing it, but the rogues have precious few unique abilities as is. the only other types that will get shifting will be Berserkers becoming animals and such. Only the rogue types will have true disguise or stealth. I don't think we will ever see spells that can duplicate this and move in on their territory.
<br />

<br />

