		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row2"><span class="name"><a name="7409"></a><b>mad sorcerer</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails"><strong></strong><br /><br /><br />Joined: 18 Oct 2001<br />Posts: 79<br />Location: Seattle</span><br /></td>
