<br />

<br />
This is how I do it. Puller calls 3 inc, I target the rear mob and cast AoE mez. I then proceed to back up a bit and wait for the tell tell signs that Mez is about to break ( you kow the ones where the mob acts like he is non aggro and stands up straight). Then either cast Mez or an AoE again. I cant tell you how many times people that have never played with a sorcerer before start to love me. As long as everyone pays attention to me calling out next target ( dont most sorcerers do that?), then all is good.
