Range is 31 paces, and Bow range and Bolts only go to 33.
<br />

<br />
It's casting time is 2 seconds, the lowest of any spell. there are only a very few at 2.2, and some at 2.5. Most spells start at 3 seconds.
<br />

<br />
It gets up to a 5 pace radius at the very highest casting, but it is damn expensive to use.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
